summary: Your house is added on a scenic cliff of Ivarstead.
descriptionHtml:
----------------
Ivarstead players house (v1.0)
----------------

Your house is added on a scenic cliff of Ivarstead.

Please be sure to back up your save file.


---
Author : hdela


---
This mod was built with Skyrim US Ver 1.7.7.0.x

Master files : Skyrim.esm, Update.esm


---
Installation : Unzip the file, and overwrite Skyrim Data folder. Or drop the esp into your Skyrim Data directory.


---
Ver: 1.0

Double bed x2
No respawn container x16
Disply case x2

Alchemy Workbench
Enchanting Workbench
Smelter Marker
BlackSmith Forge
Armor Workbench 
Blacksmith Sharpening Wheel
Tanning Rack Marker
Cooking Pot


---
Enjoy!

by hdela
author: hdela
